Welcome to Koboko Preparatory School!

Koboko Preparatory School is a nurturing and educational haven for children, welcoming both nursery and primary school pupils. We provide a stimulating and secure environment where your child can blossom and learn!

At Koboko Preparatory School, we:

  • Believe in fostering a love of learning in every child.

  • Offer a well-rounded curriculum that caters to academic, social, and emotional development.

  • Provide a safe and caring space where children feel valued and respected.

  • Have dedicated and passionate teachers who are committed to helping each child reach their full potential.

Whether your child is starting their educational journey in nursery or is ready to embark on their primary school years, Koboko Preparatory School is the perfect place for them to thrive.

Explore our website to learn more about:

  • Our curriculum and philosophy

  • Our dedicated teaching staff

  • The vibrant school environment

  • The admissions process

We warmly welcome you to our school community!

We invite you to contact us to schedule a visit and see for yourself why Koboko Preparatory School is the right choice for your child
